snippet.title: Boulder Dash for the Apple II
snippet.description:
Oh wow...this is a dissapointment...

Your character moves to fast (and I have already slowered the speed of the game for this video) and the scrolling is not as fast as your character.

To make matters worse, sometimes you start in the cave M instead of the cave A.

It is not a bad game...but certainly not a good port.
